    "Name": "Foxfire",
    "Details": "The Foxfire FXR-4R was designed around its Center Torso mounted flamer, the original purpose of even creating the ultralight BattleMech. A small laser mounted in the head provides some secondary fire for self-defense, but the 'Mechs very high movement speed is by far its best defense.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
